1
00:00:05,880 --> 00:00:08,509
♫ I want to go to the future ♫

2
00:00:08,509 --> 00:00:12,164
♫  Time bears witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,164 --> 00:00:18,257
♫ I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head ♫

4
00:00:18,257 --> 00:00:24,483
♫ I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do ♫

5
00:00:24,483 --> 00:00:30,804
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,804 --> 00:00:35,990
♫ We are always looking forward to the unknown future ♫

7
00:00:35,990 --> 00:00:43,090
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,090 --> 00:00:48,314
♫ Every day my heart beats for you ♫

9
00:00:48,314 --> 00:00:49,927
♫ Be your light ♫

10
00:00:49,927 --> 00:00:55,590
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,590 --> 00:01:02,090
♫ Every day the sun shines through the window ♫

12
00:01:02,090 --> 00:01:08,257
♫ With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight ♫

13
00:01:08,257 --> 00:01:11,744
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:17,060 --> 00:01:19,101
We're here.

15
00:01:19,862 --> 00:01:21,201
Come on. Slowly.

16
00:01:21,201 --> 00:01:23,701
- Come on, Dad.
- Slowly.

17
00:01:23,701 --> 00:01:24,942
- Slowly.
- Slowly.

18
00:01:24,942 --> 00:01:26,742
- Doudou, close the door.
- Doudou, close the door.

19
00:01:26,742 --> 00:01:28,481
Slowly, Dad.

20
00:01:28,481 --> 00:01:30,782
What are you doing? Don't take it off.

21
00:01:30,782 --> 00:01:32,482
You can't catch a cold after you have the surgery. Put it on.

22
00:01:32,482 --> 00:01:34,361
I'm about to get a heat rash.

23
00:01:34,361 --> 00:01:36,401
Dad, listen to me. Take it off when we get home.

24
00:01:36,401 --> 00:01:38,461
- I'm hot.
- We'll be home really soon.

25
00:01:38,461 --> 00:01:39,361
- Let's go.
- I'm so hot.

26
00:01:39,361 --> 00:01:41,062
We're almost—

27
00:01:41,062 --> 00:01:44,341
Welcome, welcome! A warm welcome to you!

28
00:01:44,341 --> 00:01:47,501
Welcome, welcome! A warm welcome to you!

29
00:01:47,501 --> 00:01:48,502
- Bin!
- A warm welcome to you.

30
00:01:48,502 --> 00:01:52,561
Bin, I just had a heart surgery.

31
00:01:52,561 --> 00:01:54,021
Are you all right?

32
00:01:54,021 --> 00:01:55,921
Jin, I'm sorry.

33
00:01:55,921 --> 00:01:59,462
I thought we need a sense of ritual in life.

34
00:02:00,541 --> 00:02:01,993
Gao Yang.

35
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:08,776
- Gao Yang, what are you doing?
- Get on.

36
00:02:09,200 --> 00:02:11,162
I have arms and legs. I don't need you.

37
00:02:11,162 --> 00:02:14,002
- Get up now. All right, get up.
- Get up, get up!

38
00:02:14,002 --> 00:02:16,222
- Auntie Chang, let me.
- Thank you.

39
00:02:16,222 --> 00:02:17,701
Are you happy?

40
00:02:17,701 --> 00:02:18,981
Thank you.

41
00:02:18,981 --> 00:02:20,002
Slowly. Slowly.

42
00:02:20,002 --> 00:02:22,142
Bin, I'm begging you. He just had heart surgery.

43
00:02:22,142 --> 00:02:23,900
Chang, I just want Jin to be happy.
[Episode 24: When Men Fail]

44
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:27,346
You even scared me. Make him happy? You...
[Episode 24: When Men Fail]

45
00:02:29,402 --> 00:02:30,661
Chang,

46
00:02:30,661 --> 00:02:33,402
Jin still seems pretty weak.

47
00:02:33,861 --> 00:02:35,342
Tell me about it.

48
00:02:35,342 --> 00:02:38,982
I told him not to rush home and stay a few more days in the hospital.

49
00:02:38,982 --> 00:02:40,701
He refused. He had to come home.

50
00:02:40,701 --> 00:02:46,521
I know him very well. He's just worried about the affairs in school.

51
00:02:46,521 --> 00:02:50,041
By the way, can I ask you a favor, Bin? If he asks you about what's going on in school,

52
00:02:50,041 --> 00:02:52,726
just tell him everything is fine and nothing happened.

53
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,680
Sure, sure.

54
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,403
Thank you.

55
00:03:04,222 --> 00:03:07,261
Put them in my dad's room. Let's go.

56
00:03:09,561 --> 00:03:11,297
Slowly.

57
00:03:11,297 --> 00:03:12,342
Oh, God.

58
00:03:12,342 --> 00:03:16,341
Come on. Take them off. Take them off.

59
00:03:20,362 --> 00:03:22,742
Who sent the flowers?

60
00:03:22,742 --> 00:03:24,322
Fu sent them.

61
00:03:24,322 --> 00:03:26,422
Fu? That's very considerate of him.

62
00:03:26,422 --> 00:03:28,701
Aren't you the principal?

63
00:03:36,122 --> 00:03:38,942
Bin, I heard

64
00:03:38,942 --> 00:03:42,261
Fu has been pretty demanding of you guys.

65
00:03:42,261 --> 00:03:44,122
Can you adapt to that?

66
00:03:46,620 --> 00:03:48,092
I'm all right.

67
00:03:48,934 --> 00:03:52,214
Fu is a bit strict.

68
00:03:52,214 --> 00:03:56,421
However, he cares a lot about the students.

69
00:03:56,421 --> 00:03:59,742
I... still have to take some time off.

70
00:03:59,742 --> 00:04:02,801
You... just listen to him.

71
00:04:04,340 --> 00:04:05,462
Okay.

72
00:04:05,462 --> 00:04:07,101
School is about to start.

73
00:04:07,101 --> 00:04:10,914
If anything happens in school, notify him immediately.

74
00:04:10,914 --> 00:04:13,861
Got it. Take care of yourself.

75
00:04:13,861 --> 00:04:15,641
- I'm leaving now.
- Have some water, Bin.

76
00:04:15,641 --> 00:04:17,141
No, Chang, I'm going home now.

77
00:04:17,141 --> 00:04:19,160
Why are you leaving? Stay for lunch.

78
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:22,021
No, that's all right. I hope he recovers soon.

79
00:04:22,021 --> 00:04:24,022
Gao Yang, Xiaowen, let's go.

80
00:04:24,022 --> 00:04:25,381
Sorry to trouble you, Bin.

81
00:04:25,381 --> 00:04:26,381
Don't worry about it.

82
00:04:26,381 --> 00:04:27,241
I'm leaving, Principal Jin.

83
00:04:27,241 --> 00:04:29,104
I won't see you out.

84
00:04:32,481 --> 00:04:34,801
Come on, drink some water.

85
00:04:34,801 --> 00:04:36,182
It's time to take your medicine.

86
00:04:36,182 --> 00:04:40,341
Is the school really fine?

87
00:04:40,341 --> 00:04:42,842
Didn't Bin tell you? It's fine.

88
00:04:42,842 --> 00:04:45,142
Don't worry. It's fine.

89
00:04:45,142 --> 00:04:49,761
Fu Ze said I have no muscles,

90
00:04:50,502 --> 00:04:52,642
and no qualifications.

91
00:04:55,041 --> 00:04:56,742
What are you doing, Mr. Gao?

92
00:04:56,742 --> 00:04:59,581
A new image for a new semester.

93
00:04:59,581 --> 00:05:01,684
I have to pull myself together.

94
00:05:06,622 --> 00:05:08,162
How's that?

95
00:05:08,901 --> 00:05:10,622
Not bad, right?

96
00:05:10,622 --> 00:05:14,942
Mr. Gao, did anything happen lately?

97
00:05:15,461 --> 00:05:17,332
You seem so stressed.

98
00:05:18,561 --> 00:05:20,400
There's no stress.

99
00:05:22,441 --> 00:05:25,622
That vice principal is new to the post.

100
00:05:25,622 --> 00:05:27,620
He doesn't have any trustworthy subordinates around him,

101
00:05:27,620 --> 00:05:30,781
so he asks me everything about any sports-related issues.

102
00:05:30,781 --> 00:05:33,882
An able man is always busy. I can understand that.

103
00:05:33,882 --> 00:05:38,202
But don't worry. I won't lower the standards when it comes to training.

104
00:05:38,202 --> 00:05:42,982
After all, the track and field team is my main focus. I want to take you to Beijing.

105
00:05:42,982 --> 00:05:45,497
Xiaowen, hurry up! Where's my toilet paper?

106
00:05:45,497 --> 00:05:47,642
Coming.

107
00:05:52,121 --> 00:05:53,953
Fu Ze.

108
00:06:12,162 --> 00:06:16,781
Respectable teachers, my dear students,

109
00:06:16,781 --> 00:06:20,202
a new semester means a fresh start.

110
00:06:20,801 --> 00:06:22,341
During the new semester,

111
00:06:22,341 --> 00:06:26,340
the school has set a higher standard for everyone.

112
00:06:26,340 --> 00:06:30,902
Not only for the students, but for the teachers as well.

113
00:06:30,902 --> 00:06:36,121
Teachers, you must find your new growth points in the new semester,

114
00:06:36,121 --> 00:06:41,680
- be responsible in two aspects, and self-reflect in three aspects...
- Beibei, how's Principal Jin?

115
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:48,161
- He's all right. But he still needs to rest at home for a while.
- Students of No. 3 High School are all outstanding.

116
00:06:48,161 --> 00:06:54,642
Our teachers shall strive to live up to our excellent students.

117
00:06:54,642 --> 00:06:59,162
For teachers that fail to meet the requirement, the school will deal with them seriously.

118
00:06:59,162 --> 00:07:05,502
From now on, we should treat our teachers and students equally.

119
00:07:10,984 --> 00:07:12,082
[Senior 3 Class 3]

120
00:07:12,082 --> 00:07:15,461
We already changed the door plate outside. You've all seen it. You're Seniors now.

121
00:07:15,461 --> 00:07:19,221
Set yourself straight and focus on your studies, right?

122
00:07:19,221 --> 00:07:22,942
Contain your little mishaps and control your wandering minds.

123
00:07:22,942 --> 00:07:24,781
You have to withstand the pressure and succeed.

124
00:07:24,781 --> 00:07:28,300
Otherwise, your previous ten years of schooling would be in vain, right?

125
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:29,985
Mr. Wu.

126
00:07:30,581 --> 00:07:32,384
Wait a minute.

127
00:07:34,502 --> 00:07:36,737
I have a meeting this afternoon.

128
00:07:36,737 --> 00:07:38,500
Why is Ms. Yang here?

129
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:41,201
You don't know? They're going to be together.

130
00:07:41,201 --> 00:07:42,481
Together for what?

131
00:07:42,481 --> 00:07:44,040
I put lunch in your office.

132
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,689
Okay.

133
00:07:47,341 --> 00:07:49,000
Thank you.

134
00:07:55,221 --> 00:07:57,882
Mr. Wu. What are you having for lunch, Mr. Wu?

135
00:07:57,882 --> 00:08:01,342
My lunch is... What does that have to do with you?

136
00:08:03,341 --> 00:08:06,161
Class is beginning. Open your book.

137
00:08:06,161 --> 00:08:08,341
Keep what I said in mind.

138
00:08:14,561 --> 00:08:16,324
What are you doing?

139
00:08:21,341 --> 00:08:23,206
Vice Principal,

140
00:08:25,862 --> 00:08:28,098
let me ask you something.

141
00:08:28,098 --> 00:08:30,661
Just ask.

142
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:33,561
Why did you shut the curtain?

143
00:08:33,561 --> 00:08:37,446
I heard you're planning to change the coach for the track and field team.

144
00:08:38,302 --> 00:08:39,921
Wait.

145
00:08:39,921 --> 00:08:44,501
Bin, what do you mean by this? What do you want?

146
00:08:44,501 --> 00:08:48,561
I've been doing very well with the team.

147
00:08:48,561 --> 00:08:51,542
There's a special bond between the members and me.

148
00:08:51,542 --> 00:08:55,302
I'm reluctant to leave. I'm really reluctant to leave.

149
00:08:55,302 --> 00:09:02,042
I think you're making a hasty decision. Why don't you reconsider?

150
00:09:02,042 --> 00:09:05,021
Bin, stop making useless efforts!

151
00:09:07,142 --> 00:09:10,022
By the way, Jia, didn't you say your dad called you?

152
00:09:10,022 --> 00:09:12,276
How did it go? Did you find him?

153
00:09:13,981 --> 00:09:18,242
H-He's still unwilling to see me.

154
00:09:18,802 --> 00:09:21,017
Well, we won't see each other then.

155
00:09:22,721 --> 00:09:24,382
Jia, eat something. It's yummy.

156
00:09:24,382 --> 00:09:29,201
I-I-I'm fine. A-Aunt is all I need.

157
00:09:29,701 --> 00:09:32,461
Just cheer up. No matter what, I'll look for him with you.

158
00:09:32,461 --> 00:09:34,328
We'll certainly find him.

159
00:09:34,942 --> 00:09:36,829
I'll go ask them about a problem.

160
00:09:37,782 --> 00:09:41,541
Xiaowen, I don't know how to solve this problem. Can you teach me?

161
00:09:41,541 --> 00:09:42,902
Wait in line. Xiaowen is teaching me.

162
00:09:42,902 --> 00:09:44,542
I don't understand it either. Teach me too.

163
00:09:44,542 --> 00:09:46,557
Wait a minute. I'll get to you soon.

164
00:09:47,653 --> 00:09:49,101
- Hello, Vice Principal.
- Hello.

165
00:09:49,101 --> 00:09:50,673
- Hello, Principal.
- Hello.

166
00:09:50,673 --> 00:09:52,826
Principal, you're going home?

167
00:09:53,221 --> 00:09:55,562
- Let me see you off.
- No, we're not going in the same direction.

168
00:09:55,562 --> 00:09:58,262
- Here you go.
- What is it?

169
00:09:58,262 --> 00:10:01,002
Well, you've been working hard all day.

170
00:10:01,002 --> 00:10:02,821
Have a drink and relax a little when you go home.

171
00:10:02,821 --> 00:10:06,402
Bin, what are you doing this for? Are you trying to bribe me?

172
00:10:06,402 --> 00:10:08,681
That won't do. I will never accept it!

173
00:10:08,681 --> 00:10:09,902
Take your hands off me.

174
00:10:09,902 --> 00:10:13,902
What are you talking about? It's not that serious. Just two bottles.

175
00:10:13,902 --> 00:10:17,941
Don't do this! I-I-I can't take them. Definitely not.

176
00:10:17,941 --> 00:10:19,022
You really don't want them?

177
00:10:19,022 --> 00:10:20,652
I really don't want them.

178
00:10:22,142 --> 00:10:24,242
Fine. I understand.

179
00:10:24,242 --> 00:10:27,640
How can I take them? If I take them, that would be...

180
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:29,282
Reconsider your choice for the coach!

181
00:10:29,282 --> 00:10:32,701
Gao Bin! That's ridiculous!

182
00:10:33,701 --> 00:10:36,681
♪ Let's drink to our heart's content today ♪

183
00:10:36,681 --> 00:10:37,621
You're home?

184
00:10:37,621 --> 00:10:38,701
You made these?

185
00:10:38,701 --> 00:10:40,001
I bought them.

186
00:10:40,001 --> 00:10:41,421
You're wasting money again.

187
00:10:41,421 --> 00:10:43,121
Let's eat.

188
00:10:43,121 --> 00:10:46,102
What's the happy occasion, Mr. Gao?

189
00:10:46,102 --> 00:10:49,821
Xiaowen, I took care of the Vice Principal.

190
00:10:49,821 --> 00:10:54,482
Took care of him for what? Didn't you say he trusts you?

191
00:10:55,182 --> 00:10:58,182
Yes. He just trusts me back, then.

192
00:10:58,182 --> 00:11:00,881
Now, our relationship has advanced to the next level.

193
00:11:00,881 --> 00:11:03,162
We're buddies now.

194
00:11:04,062 --> 00:11:07,101
Xiaowen, the qualifying competition is about to begin.

195
00:11:07,101 --> 00:11:12,002
I will surely lead you out of Tieyuan and head straight to Beijing.

196
00:11:12,002 --> 00:11:16,982
Keep boasting. Don't get carried away or he might remove you from the coach position.

197
00:11:16,982 --> 00:11:19,461
That's the last thing he'll do.

198
00:11:19,461 --> 00:11:22,862
Gao Yang, I'm telling you, the vice principal is my buddy.

199
00:11:22,862 --> 00:11:24,341
We're like brothers, you know?

200
00:11:24,341 --> 00:11:27,181
Yeah, right. Let's eat.

201
00:11:27,181 --> 00:11:28,815
Let's eat.

202
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:56,381
W-Who is it?

203
00:12:02,741 --> 00:12:04,802
Someone's following you?

204
00:12:05,522 --> 00:12:08,201
I-I'm not sure.

205
00:12:08,201 --> 00:12:10,280
Maybe I'm just overthinking.

206
00:12:10,280 --> 00:12:12,980
Gao Yang and I will take you home after school.

207
00:12:13,461 --> 00:12:16,182
That's okay. I'm fine.

208
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:19,621
Is everyone here?

209
00:12:19,621 --> 00:12:23,301
Do your warm ups. We'll officially begin in ten minutes.

210
00:12:25,621 --> 00:12:28,982
Mr. Gao, come here.

211
00:12:28,982 --> 00:12:30,660
Keep training.

212
00:12:32,561 --> 00:12:35,442
- Vice Principal.
- Keep your distance.

213
00:12:35,942 --> 00:12:37,621
Take this.

214
00:12:38,081 --> 00:12:40,341
- Take it.
- But...

215
00:12:41,182 --> 00:12:44,982
Our school does not tolerate misconduct like giving and receiving bribes.

216
00:12:44,982 --> 00:12:47,301
- Vice Principal...
- I'm not finished yet.

217
00:12:47,301 --> 00:12:49,461
I'm formally notifying you.

218
00:12:49,461 --> 00:12:52,942
From now on, Mr. Li will be the coach of the track and field team.

219
00:12:52,942 --> 00:12:55,601
Get back to your own work.

220
00:12:56,382 --> 00:13:00,161
Don't do this again. Times have changed.

221
00:13:10,542 --> 00:13:12,165
Mr. Gao.

222
00:13:12,701 --> 00:13:14,276
What's wrong?

223
00:13:15,160 --> 00:13:18,848
Vice Principal just came to talk to me about something.

224
00:13:24,142 --> 00:13:26,221
I gave him a gift last time, right?

225
00:13:26,221 --> 00:13:29,742
This is his gift in return. Courtesy demands reciprocity.

226
00:13:30,302 --> 00:13:32,521
It's all right. Go back to training. Go on.

227
00:14:06,182 --> 00:14:08,401
That's it for today's training.

228
00:14:08,401 --> 00:14:09,921
Dismiss.

229
00:14:26,501 --> 00:14:29,024
That's why we must have three sets of solutions.

230
00:14:29,660 --> 00:14:32,402
Fu Ze! I won't accept that!

231
00:14:32,402 --> 00:14:35,741
- Should I... let you two talk?
- That's not necessary.

232
00:14:35,741 --> 00:14:39,861
Li, take a seat. It's all right. Take a seat.

233
00:14:39,861 --> 00:14:43,262
Mr. Gao Bin, I've already decided on the coach of the track and field team.

234
00:14:43,262 --> 00:14:44,701
Don't dawdle here.

235
00:14:44,701 --> 00:14:47,622
Give me a reason! I've had twenty years of teaching experience.

236
00:14:47,622 --> 00:14:50,461
How many teachers in the No.3 High School have been here longer than me?

237
00:14:50,461 --> 00:14:53,302
How am I unworthy to be the coach? Tell me!

238
00:14:53,302 --> 00:14:59,840
Bin, I didn't tell you everything because I've taken your twenty years of teaching experience into consideration!

239
00:14:59,840 --> 00:15:03,442
I'm begging you! Don't take that into consideration. Just say it!

240
00:15:03,442 --> 00:15:06,442
- I'm begging you!
- Bin, would you just leave?

241
00:15:06,442 --> 00:15:09,502
I'm begging you! Just be out with it! How am I worse than Li?

242
00:15:09,502 --> 00:15:12,322
- Maybe I should leave.
- Sit down.

243
00:15:18,861 --> 00:15:21,382
Fu Ze, tell me.

244
00:15:21,382 --> 00:15:26,181
Tell me directly. Just speak your mind!

245
00:15:26,181 --> 00:15:29,821
- Fine, I'll tell you then!
- Go ahead!

246
00:15:29,821 --> 00:15:32,481
Jin only gave you that position because he's looking out for you.

247
00:15:32,481 --> 00:15:35,101
He's under a huge amount of pressure!

248
00:15:35,101 --> 00:15:37,470
The No.3 High School finally got a chance to participate in the national competitions.

249
00:15:37,470 --> 00:15:39,860
Our superiors are taking it very seriously.

250
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:44,722
Look at you, you have no academic title or any awards. You have nothing!

251
00:15:44,722 --> 00:15:46,302
Do you know how many teachers asked me,

252
00:15:46,302 --> 00:15:50,422
"Vice Principal Fu, why don't you let the best PE teacher in No.3 High School to be the coach?"

253
00:15:50,422 --> 00:15:52,782
I was rendered speechless!

254
00:15:52,782 --> 00:15:57,301
You can see that now. This is the best PE teacher of our school!

255
00:15:57,301 --> 00:15:59,401
Why should I let you do it?

256
00:16:01,422 --> 00:16:03,232
Give me the keys.

257
00:16:03,701 --> 00:16:05,529
Give me the keys.

258
00:16:08,220 --> 00:16:11,476
What are you doing? Are you trying to start a tug-of-war with me?

259
00:16:11,476 --> 00:16:15,802
I'm telling you, I used to be a national level Class II athlete.

260
00:16:17,701 --> 00:16:19,622
Give it to me.

261
00:16:19,622 --> 00:16:20,770
- Give it to me.
- Vice Principal.

262
00:16:20,770 --> 00:16:22,430
Give it to me.

263
00:16:26,845 --> 00:16:28,782
- Vice Principal!
- What happened?

264
00:16:28,782 --> 00:16:30,461
What happened here? Why are you fighting?

265
00:16:30,461 --> 00:16:32,942
- What do you want?
- I want to be the coach!

266
00:16:32,942 --> 00:16:34,641
- What else do you want?
- I just want to be the coach!

267
00:16:34,641 --> 00:16:37,441
- What else do you want?
- I want to be the coach!

268
00:16:37,441 --> 00:16:39,302
Why should you?

269
00:16:39,302 --> 00:16:44,062
All you do is slouch in that equipment room of the PE department every day!

270
00:16:44,062 --> 00:16:46,142
You smell like stinky socks!

271
00:16:46,142 --> 00:16:49,262
You don't even know if you can still teach,

272
00:16:49,262 --> 00:16:51,762
and you want to coach the team?

273
00:16:51,762 --> 00:16:53,942
Let me tell you one last time.

274
00:16:53,942 --> 00:16:57,582
I'm the principal. I demand that you give me the keys!

275
00:16:57,582 --> 00:16:58,701
No.

276
00:16:58,701 --> 00:17:00,442
- Will you give it to me or not?
- No!

277
00:17:00,442 --> 00:17:02,140
- Will you give it to me or not?
- No!

278
00:17:02,140 --> 00:17:03,296
I...

279
00:17:03,296 --> 00:17:05,561
- Don't get physical.
- Principal! Let's discuss it nicely!

280
00:17:05,561 --> 00:17:07,822
What are you guys doing? What's going on?

281
00:17:07,822 --> 00:17:10,161
- Enough.
- Don't fight.

282
00:17:10,161 --> 00:17:11,080
Vice Principal!

283
00:17:11,080 --> 00:17:12,872
Mr. Gao,

284
00:17:15,741 --> 00:17:17,461
let him have it.

285
00:17:29,942 --> 00:17:31,686
Xiaowen,

286
00:17:34,620 --> 00:17:37,403
- but I promised you...
- Mr. Gao,

287
00:17:39,494 --> 00:17:42,163
let's go home.

288
00:17:52,500 --> 00:17:54,441
What are you guys doing?

289
00:17:57,862 --> 00:17:59,902
Why isn't he talking?

290
00:18:01,482 --> 00:18:04,672
The school won't let Mr. Gao coach the track and field team anymore.

291
00:18:06,330 --> 00:18:09,200
He got laid off?

292
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:11,340
Mr. Gao.

293
00:18:11,340 --> 00:18:12,797
Mr. Gao.

294
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:17,880
Hello, Mr. Gao.

295
00:18:28,622 --> 00:18:31,862
Mr. Gao, are you okay?

296
00:18:35,780 --> 00:18:37,288
Let me.

297
00:18:38,021 --> 00:18:39,734
Bin!

298
00:18:40,862 --> 00:18:42,606
Bin!

299
00:18:43,342 --> 00:18:44,942
It's not a big deal.

300
00:18:44,942 --> 00:18:47,161
There's always Principal Jin.

301
00:18:50,310 --> 00:18:52,701
Come out for dinner.

302
00:18:52,701 --> 00:18:57,161
Well, Xiaowen is making dumplings for us.

303
00:19:01,220 --> 00:19:04,601
Come watch a game, or play cards.

304
00:19:08,321 --> 00:19:10,322
This should be enough.

305
00:19:12,340 --> 00:19:16,182
Mr. Gao, it's fine if you want some time alone.

306
00:19:16,182 --> 00:19:19,642
Gao Yang and I will go out for a while.

307
00:19:28,081 --> 00:19:30,321
Is Gao Bin that bad?

308
00:19:30,321 --> 00:19:32,201
Why must they change the coach?

309
00:19:34,422 --> 00:19:37,461
The school has its reasons.

310
00:19:38,102 --> 00:19:40,121
Over all these years,

311
00:19:40,942 --> 00:19:43,762
he has tried the most this time.

312
00:19:48,021 --> 00:19:52,741
I was planning to tell my dad about that,

313
00:19:53,221 --> 00:19:56,102
but my mom said my dad can't be irritated anymore.

314
00:19:56,102 --> 00:19:59,722
She won't let me tell him about any school-related matter.

315
00:20:00,501 --> 00:20:02,021
Principal Jin can't do anything about it even if he knows.

316
00:20:02,021 --> 00:20:04,190
Let him recuperate in peace.

317
00:20:07,981 --> 00:20:10,621
How is Mr. Gao now?

318
00:20:10,621 --> 00:20:12,942
Our teammates are really concerned about him.

319
00:20:12,942 --> 00:20:16,322
H-He isn't coming to school anymore?

320
00:20:17,422 --> 00:20:20,201
He hasn't eaten in days.

321
00:20:27,622 --> 00:20:28,741
Uncle Zhang,

322
00:20:28,741 --> 00:20:32,861
I'll bring you your pants tomorrow after I mend them. Go home now.

323
00:20:54,820 --> 00:20:57,861
What are you doing? Come back here!

324
00:21:08,444 --> 00:21:11,564
[Senior Class 3]

325
00:21:44,781 --> 00:21:47,261
Aunt, I'm home.

326
00:21:48,301 --> 00:21:53,881
Jia, do you feel like someone's been following you lately?

327
00:21:55,182 --> 00:21:59,382
I think... there is.

328
00:21:59,981 --> 00:22:03,701
He's wearing a hat and a mask?

329
00:22:03,701 --> 00:22:08,022
I-I can't remember it very well. W-What's wrong, Aunt?

330
00:22:08,022 --> 00:22:10,042
He must be your dad.

331
00:22:10,541 --> 00:22:16,521
When I was walking home last night, I just felt like someone was staring at me from behind.

332
00:22:16,521 --> 00:22:20,381
I suddenly looked back and saw him following behind me furtively.

333
00:22:20,381 --> 00:22:24,902
I can recognize him from his height and the way he walks no matter how he tried to disguise himself.

334
00:22:24,902 --> 00:22:27,370
Mi Daqiang, it was him for sure.

335
00:22:27,814 --> 00:22:30,562
W-W-Well... What should we do, Aunt?

336
00:22:31,221 --> 00:22:33,111
What should we do?

337
00:22:35,862 --> 00:22:39,041
Come on, come with me. Let's go. Hurry.

338
00:22:39,041 --> 00:22:41,999
- Let's go.
- Where are we going?

339
00:22:53,820 --> 00:22:55,662
Mr. Gao,

340
00:22:55,662 --> 00:22:57,801
you haven't eaten in days.

341
00:22:57,801 --> 00:22:59,881
Come out and eat something.

342
00:23:00,522 --> 00:23:03,361
I'll go to Beijing to stay with my mom.

343
00:23:03,942 --> 00:23:05,877
Aren't you going to stop me?

344
00:23:10,182 --> 00:23:12,049
I ran out of ideas. Let's eat.

345
00:23:14,021 --> 00:23:15,202
Who is it?

346
00:23:15,202 --> 00:23:17,921
It's me, Mi Jia's aunt.

347
00:23:23,221 --> 00:23:24,952
Thank you.

348
00:23:25,622 --> 00:23:27,942
- Have some water first, Aunt.
- Okay.

349
00:23:30,261 --> 00:23:32,061
What is it?

350
00:23:33,061 --> 00:23:35,902
I can't discuss this matter with you boys.

351
00:23:35,902 --> 00:23:37,981
Go tell your dad to come.

352
00:23:40,822 --> 00:23:43,122
Mi Jia, what's going on?

353
00:23:43,122 --> 00:23:46,122
My dad... i-is back.

354
00:23:48,962 --> 00:23:55,002
H-He was the one who was stalking us before.

355
00:23:55,002 --> 00:23:57,921
Aunt almost caught him yesterday.

356
00:23:58,622 --> 00:24:01,742
Hurry, tell your dad to come out now.

357
00:24:01,742 --> 00:24:05,501
If we wait, Mi Daqiang might run away.

358
00:24:08,142 --> 00:24:11,361
Aunt, Mr. Gao has something to do these days.

359
00:24:11,361 --> 00:24:13,061
Maybe we can help you?

360
00:24:13,061 --> 00:24:14,501
That's right.

361
00:24:14,501 --> 00:24:16,401
That's not going to work.

362
00:24:17,021 --> 00:24:19,442
How unfortunate.

363
00:24:19,442 --> 00:24:21,541
Forget it. I'll go find someone else.

364
00:24:21,541 --> 00:24:23,021
- Wait, Aunt.
- What?

365
00:24:23,021 --> 00:24:24,699
Please stay.

366
00:24:27,242 --> 00:24:31,021
We can't give such an arduous task to just anyone.

367
00:24:31,021 --> 00:24:37,342
I think we must find a mature and prudent man like Gao Bin

368
00:24:37,342 --> 00:24:40,961
to finish this task, right?

369
00:24:40,961 --> 00:24:43,822
Mr. Gao is the backbone of our family.

370
00:24:43,822 --> 00:24:46,942
Without him, we wouldn't even know what to do.

371
00:24:53,541 --> 00:24:55,195
Mr. Gao.

372
00:24:58,461 --> 00:25:02,022
Aunt, don't worry.

373
00:25:02,022 --> 00:25:04,206
Leave this to me.

374
00:25:10,420 --> 00:25:12,182
This is Aunt's house.

375
00:25:12,182 --> 00:25:14,820
There are three intersections to her house.

376
00:25:14,820 --> 00:25:17,102
The three of us will guard each of these intersections.

377
00:25:17,102 --> 00:25:20,642
If any suspicious individuals appear, we'll notify each other right away.

378
00:25:20,642 --> 00:25:22,760
We'll surround him.

379
00:25:22,761 --> 00:25:25,450
He would never be able to escape.

380
00:25:25,822 --> 00:25:27,801
It's as simple as that.

381
00:25:31,182 --> 00:25:33,982
By the way, we're decent people.

382
00:25:33,982 --> 00:25:37,321
Try to do this without getting physical.

383
00:25:41,482 --> 00:25:43,881
Do you guys understand?

384
00:25:44,561 --> 00:25:47,861
Sure. Let's eat. I'm starving.

385
00:25:55,401 --> 00:25:58,681
Is he having terminal lucidity?

386
00:25:59,741 --> 00:26:01,221
Delicious.

387
00:26:01,221 --> 00:26:03,020
Mr. Gao,

388
00:26:04,121 --> 00:26:05,662
are you okay?

389
00:26:05,662 --> 00:26:07,609
What could be wrong with me?

390
00:26:11,660 --> 00:26:15,894
I've figured out the matter in school.

391
00:26:15,894 --> 00:26:18,881
Would pride put meals on the table? No.

392
00:26:19,342 --> 00:26:21,080
After I solve

393
00:26:21,080 --> 00:26:23,442
the matter of Mi Jia's dad,

394
00:26:23,442 --> 00:26:26,700
I'll go back to school and earn money.

395
00:26:26,700 --> 00:26:28,981
They won't let me be the coach. Fine, I won't be the coach.

396
00:26:28,981 --> 00:26:32,382
I'll be an assistant for Li or something.

397
00:26:32,382 --> 00:26:35,400
What's so bad about that? It's not a big deal.

398
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:37,304
So delicious.

399
00:26:39,102 --> 00:26:40,662
What are you guys doing?

400
00:26:40,662 --> 00:26:42,450
Come have dinner.

401
00:26:43,902 --> 00:26:45,761
Let's eat.

402
00:26:47,261 --> 00:26:50,301
But I think there's a bug in your plan.

403
00:26:50,301 --> 00:26:52,342
How will we communicate with each other?

404
00:26:52,342 --> 00:26:53,741
I have tricks up my sleeves.

405
00:26:53,741 --> 00:26:55,369
What?

406
00:26:56,081 --> 00:26:58,501
I have tricks up my sleeves!

407
00:26:58,501 --> 00:27:00,671
Hurry up and eat.

408
00:27:05,261 --> 00:27:09,861
At first, I didn't want to mention that ungrateful man.

409
00:27:09,861 --> 00:27:13,762
He has wronged me, and he even has wronged you more.

410
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:20,700
Over these years, I just treat myself like I don't have a brother.

411
00:27:20,700 --> 00:27:24,681
However, if he's back now,

412
00:27:24,681 --> 00:27:30,881
I think I should still show you what he looks like.

413
00:27:34,762 --> 00:27:37,942
T-T-This is my dad?

414
00:27:39,561 --> 00:27:41,822
A-Aunt,

415
00:27:41,822 --> 00:27:45,562
do you think we look alike?

416
00:27:45,562 --> 00:27:48,921
You probably look more like your mom.

417
00:27:48,921 --> 00:27:52,922
The two of them met at a disco bar.

418
00:27:52,922 --> 00:27:55,561
I've never met your mom.

419
00:27:55,561 --> 00:27:57,822
She hasn't contacted us either.

420
00:27:57,822 --> 00:28:03,562
I had to ask someone else to find out Mi Daqiang had a child out there.

421
00:28:03,562 --> 00:28:05,541
H-He even abandoned you!

422
00:28:05,541 --> 00:28:08,462
I didn't even know where to look for you.

423
00:28:08,462 --> 00:28:11,582
It wasn't until Mr. Gao posted the missing persons notice

424
00:28:11,582 --> 00:28:16,662
that I realized the time and the events match up.

425
00:28:16,662 --> 00:28:19,882
Our surname Mi is very rare.

426
00:28:19,882 --> 00:28:22,601
That's how I found you.

427
00:28:27,981 --> 00:28:34,802
Jia, over the years, he has never raised you.

428
00:28:34,802 --> 00:28:38,582
When Mr. Gao catches him tomorrow,

429
00:28:38,582 --> 00:28:42,102
I'll surely make him apologize to you.

430
00:28:50,519 --> 00:28:53,541
Testing, testing. Fried Pork, please reply when you hear this.

431
00:28:53,541 --> 00:28:56,982
Fried Pork copy. How's Clear Noodles?

432
00:28:56,982 --> 00:28:58,342
Clear Noodles is fine.

433
00:28:58,342 --> 00:29:01,922
Dumplings, what if Mi Jia's dad doesn't show up today?

434
00:29:01,922 --> 00:29:04,221
We'll continue tomorrow. This mission must be completed.

435
00:29:04,221 --> 00:29:06,741
We pledge to complete the mission.

436
00:29:06,741 --> 00:29:08,186
Let's move.

437
00:29:52,342 --> 00:29:55,041
Clear Noodles, any updates there?

438
00:29:55,041 --> 00:29:57,442
Nothing at the present, over.

439
00:30:15,781 --> 00:30:19,822
Aunt already walked around a few times. Did Mi Daqiang run away?

440
00:30:20,342 --> 00:30:22,861
Don't speak. Keep an eye on it.

441
00:30:22,861 --> 00:30:24,692
Copy that.

442
00:30:31,300 --> 00:30:34,841
Dumplings, do you want dumplings for lunch?

443
00:30:34,841 --> 00:30:37,647
No more chit chat. Don't expose yourself.

444
00:30:53,820 --> 00:30:56,821
Aunt is tired. Let's pack it up.

445
00:31:14,260 --> 00:31:15,670
Here.

446
00:31:17,780 --> 00:31:21,001
Start eating. Why aren't you eating anything?

447
00:31:21,541 --> 00:31:25,404
Aunt, we weren't able to catch him.

448
00:31:25,404 --> 00:31:28,581
It's not right for us to bum meals off you all the time.

449
00:31:31,282 --> 00:31:33,138
Mr. Gao,

450
00:31:33,138 --> 00:31:36,541
I think Mi Daqiang must've run away.

451
00:31:36,541 --> 00:31:39,441
Look, he came back to see her.

452
00:31:39,442 --> 00:31:42,681
She's already big enough to go to college.

453
00:31:42,681 --> 00:31:46,481
He would have to pay her tuition. He must've regretted it.

454
00:31:48,500 --> 00:31:50,002
- Let's eat.
- Come on.

455
00:31:50,002 --> 00:31:52,561
Start eating. It's getting cold.

456
00:31:52,561 --> 00:31:55,779
Come, Jia. Eat it while it's hot.

457
00:32:01,260 --> 00:32:03,131
Mr. Gao,

458
00:32:03,501 --> 00:32:05,242
Xiaowen,

459
00:32:05,981 --> 00:32:07,834
Gao Yang,

460
00:32:07,834 --> 00:32:10,840
thank you for today.

461
00:32:11,481 --> 00:32:13,122
Thank you for your efforts.

462
00:32:13,122 --> 00:32:16,542
Well... Mi Jia, please don't say that.

463
00:32:16,542 --> 00:32:19,842
We didn't do anything at all.

464
00:32:19,842 --> 00:32:21,524
That's right.

465
00:32:22,161 --> 00:32:27,461
You don't have to go through the trouble of looking for my dad anymore.

466
00:32:29,862 --> 00:32:32,522
This time, I've really given up.

467
00:32:44,261 --> 00:32:48,042
Aunt... we haven't helped much today and you still treated us with such hospitality.

468
00:32:48,042 --> 00:32:50,361
We're so embarrassed.

469
00:32:50,361 --> 00:32:52,900
All right, no need to see us off. It's getting late.

470
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:56,422
Mr. Gao, thank you so much this time.

471
00:32:56,422 --> 00:32:58,822
I just heard from Jia that you're no longer the coach of the team.

472
00:32:58,822 --> 00:33:03,321
Look, I still caused you so much trouble. I'm really...

473
00:33:03,321 --> 00:33:05,722
Aunt, I would certainly help you

474
00:33:05,722 --> 00:33:09,481
even if I get laid off, let alone not being the coach anymore.

475
00:33:15,221 --> 00:33:17,461
All right, Aunt, we're leaving now.

476
00:33:17,461 --> 00:33:18,781
Sorry to trouble you.

477
00:33:18,781 --> 00:33:21,948
Mr. Gao, that person seems off.

478
00:33:21,948 --> 00:33:23,221
What's wrong?

479
00:33:23,221 --> 00:33:24,977
Who is that?

480
00:33:26,781 --> 00:33:28,761
- Stop right there!
- Stop right there!

481
00:33:28,761 --> 00:33:30,442
Mr. Gao!

482
00:33:30,442 --> 00:33:31,781
- What's wrong?
- Protect them.

483
00:33:31,781 --> 00:33:33,722
Be careful!

484
00:33:35,582 --> 00:33:37,702
Could he be Mi Daqiang?

485
00:33:37,702 --> 00:33:42,022
Aunt, Mi Jia, don't worry. They can catch him for sure.

486
00:33:42,022 --> 00:33:44,461
Run, keep running!

487
00:33:44,461 --> 00:33:46,600
How will you escape?

488
00:34:13,940 --> 00:34:20,072
♫ I know the direction of dawn ♫

489
00:34:20,072 --> 00:34:27,437
♫ It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine ♫

490
00:34:27,437 --> 00:34:33,427
♫  The starlight that shines along the way  ♫

491
00:34:33,427 --> 00:34:39,367
♫ Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams into my heart ♫

492
00:34:39,367 --> 00:34:46,119
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

493
00:34:46,119 --> 00:34:51,659
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

494
00:34:51,659 --> 00:34:55,672
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

495
00:34:55,672 --> 00:34:59,094
♫  Let set sail on our dreams  ♫

496
00:34:59,094 --> 00:35:02,389
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

497
00:35:02,389 --> 00:35:09,049
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, I'll be by your side  ♫

498
00:35:09,049 --> 00:35:12,360
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

499
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:16,572
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

500
00:35:16,572 --> 00:35:20,392
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

501
00:35:20,392 --> 00:35:28,352
♫ And go straight forward without any sorrow ♫
